data.name: grdResult.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT C.PKCPL3020 PKCPL3020, DECODE(C.HANGMOG_CODE, C.SOURCE_GUMSA, '', ' ') || D.GUMSA_NAME GUMSA_NAME, C.STANDARD_YN STANDARD_YN, C.CPL_RESULT CPL_RESULT, C.CONFIRM_YN CONFIRM_YN, C.BEFORE_RESULT BEFORE_RESULT, C.PANIC_YN PANIC_YN, C.DELTA_YN DELTA_YN, E.CODE_NAME DANUI_NAME, DECODE(C.TO_STANDARD,NULL,C.FROM_STANDARD,C.FROM_STANDARD || ' ~ ' || C.TO_STANDARD) STANDARD, C.COMMENTS COMMENTS, DECODE(A.IN_OUT_GUBUN,'I',A.FKOCS2003,A.FKOCS1003) FKOCS, C.FKCPL2010 FKCPL2010, C.LAB_NO LAB_NO, C.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE, C.SPECIMEN_CODE SPECIMEN_CODE, C.EMERGENCY EMERGENCY, C.GUMSAJA GUMSAJA, A.BUNHO BUNHO, C.RESULT_DATE RESULT_DATE, :f_specimen_ser SPECIMEN_SER, C.RESULT_FORM RESULT_FORM, C.SOURCE_GUMSA SOURCE_GUMSA, D.GROUP_GUBUN GROUP_GUBUN, C.SOURCE_GUMSA GROUP_HANGMOG, NVL(C.DISPLAY_YN,'Y') DISPLAY_YN, LPAD(C.FKCPL2010,10,'0')||LPAD(C.PKCPL3020,10,'0') KEY FROM CPL0109 E, CPL0101 D, CPL3020 C, CPL2010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE(+) = D.HOSP_CODE AND C.LAB_NO = :f_lab_no AND A.SPECIMEN_SER = :f_specimen_ser AND A.JUNDAL_GUBUN = :f_jundal_gubun AND A.PKCPL2010 = C.FKCPL2010 AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = D.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.SPECIMEN_CODE = D.SPECIMEN_CODE AND C.EMERGENCY = D.EMERGENCY AND E.CODE(+) = D.DANUI AND E.CODE_TYPE(+) = '03' ORDER BY C.PKCPL3020

data.name: grdPa.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT SUBSTR(A.LAB_NO,7,4) LAB_NO , C.SUNAME , A.SPECIMEN_SER , A.LAB_NO LAB_SORT, A.PART_JUBSU_DATE , A.JUNDAL_GUBUN , :f_gubun GUBUN, FN_CPL_SPECIMEN_SER_RESULT_YN (A.SPECIMEN_SER,:f_jundal_gubun) RESULT_YN, FN_CPL_SPECIMEN_SER_CONFIRM_YN(A.SPECIMEN_SER,:f_jundal_gubun) CONFIRM_YN FROM OUT0101 C, CPL2010 B, CPL3010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.PART_JUBSU_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_from_date,'YYYY/MM/DD') AND TO_DATE(:f_to_date,'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.JUNDAL_GUBUN = :f_jundal_gubun AND B.SPECIMEN_SER = A.SPECIMEN_SER AND ( :f_gubun = 'Y' OR :f_gubun = 'N' AND FN_CPL_SPECIMEN_SER_CONFIRM_YN(A.SPECIMEN_SER,:f_jundal_gubun) <> 'Y') --AND FN_CPL_SPECIMEN_SER_CONFIRM_YN(A.SPECIMEN_SER,:f_jundal_gubun) LIKE DECODE(:f_gubun,'Y','%',:f_gubun) AND C.BUNHO = B.BUNHO ORDER BY LAB_NO
